energy saving
=============

# settings
ASPM L0s	low resume latency, power saving standby state
ASPM L1		higher resume latency, more power saving standby state
ASPM L0sL1	both L0s and L1 enabled

# going from PCI-E 3.0 Gen 3 to Gen 1 (saves ca. 2W idle power)
DMI Max Link Speed
PEG Port Configuration
PCH Configuration -> PCI Express Configuration

